<plot>Jane loses her job and has to move in with her brother Paul, who lives in the house of their deceased parents. Paul isn't happy about his alcoholic sister's intrusion into his orderly, godly life. Jane hides a secret, hoping that her brother will see her for who she truly is and love her despite her shortcomings. When the secret is revealed, Paul's eyes are opened to an unexpected reality that will change his life forever.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?335650</url></doc>
